Ba a yawan samun ƙananan matsin yanayi a Arizona ba, amma hakan zai faru ne a farkon mako mai zuwa, sa'ad da guguwar Rose ta yi amfani da makamashi mai yawa a cikin hamada a kudu maso yammacin Amirka, kuma hakan zai iya jawo ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta riga ta ba da gargadi game da ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona da kuma kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
