Sabbin samfurori na Cibiyar Hurricane ta Amirka sun yi hasashen cewa za a yi ruwan sama mai tsawon santimita 5 da 10 a Mogollon Rim, Arizona.
Wasu sassan hamada a kudu maso yammacin Amirka, har da tsakiyar Dutsen Rocky da Great Basin, suna iya samun ruwan sama mai tsawon santimita 2.5 da santimita 5 da haɗarin zuwa santimita 10.
A yankunan da babu haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa, ruwan ruwan da ke ruwan Rosa zai iya zama albarka, domin yankin yana fama da fari.
