A cewar Hukumar Kula da Rashin Gwaninta ta Amirka, fiye da kashi 40 cikin ɗari na Arizona tana fama da matsanancin fari, na biyu mafi girma, weather.com ta ruwaito.
Guguwar Rosa za ta fara tafiya a yankin Baja California na Mexico.
