Rosa za ta yi tafiya a arewacin Mexico a matsayin guguwar ruwan sama kuma ta kai iyakar Arizona da sanyin safiyar Talata a matsayin matsanancin yanayi, wanda zai bi ta Arizona zuwa kudancin Utah a ƙarshen yammacin Talata.
