A wannan karon kuma, 'yan wasan Rangers sun kasa magance matsalar da Jacob ya samu.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya dace da Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai natsuwa kuma ya zaɓi Menga don ƙarasa mai sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu lokacin da ya canza Coulibaly zuwa Ryan Kent kuma canjin ya yi tasiri kusan nan take lokacin da farfajiya ta buga ƙwallon zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe ƙoƙarin.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da sa abokan hamayyarsa su yi wasa daidai da irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna yin dogon wasa bayan dogon wasa.
A lokacin da Holt ya yi nasara, zai iya ƙarfafa jagorancinsa a mataki na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya yi nasara wajen hana Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya fita daga kusurwa.
Glenn Middleton, mai maye gurbin Rangers, ya yi wani gagarumin bukatar hukunci a lokacin da ya yi karo da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
