Johnny English Strikes Again - Ba shi da iko ba ɗan leƙen asiri na Rowan Atkinson
Yanzu al'ada ce a nemi kyautar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da yanayin Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya zama daidai da wannan sabon fim na sabon wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English - jerin abubuwan da suka shafi 'yan leƙen asiri da aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma aka sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin za a yi wa mutane ba'a game da yadda mugaye muke zama sabon abin da ƙasar ta fitar?
Ko ta yaya, an sake ba da lasisin sake wa Johnny English mai ƙwarewa da fuskar roba lasisi na sake sakewa a karo na biyu - sunansa ya nuna fiye da kowane abu cewa shi babban hali ne mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don buga haruffa har ma a ƙasashen da ba Turanci ba
Hakika, shi ne babban jami'in asirin da ya ba da kyauta ga Clouseau, da Mr. Bean, da kuma ɗan ƙaramin ɗan wasan daga bikin buɗe gasar Olympics a London 2012.
An kuma yi shi ne a asali bisa wannan matafiyi da kuma mutumin da ke da ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya yi a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta da su wanda ke haifar da rikici a duk inda ya tafi.
Akwai wasu lokatai masu kyau a cikin fim din JE na baya-bayan nan
Ina son ganin Johnny English yana zuwa kusa da wani helikofta sanye da takalmin ƙarni na tsakiya, kuma lokacin da takardar mai juyawa ta ɗan gajeren lokaci ta buge shi.
Atkins yana da baiwa don wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma yanayin ya zama mai ɗan ƙarancin gaske kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman saboda manyan kamfanonin fim kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu yanzu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Kuma ina ganin cewa ba'a dace da yara ba maimakon manya, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ba ya da ban mamaki a cikin zane-zane kamar yadda Atkins ya yi a fim dinsa a matsayin Bean.
Yanzu, batun da ke ci gaba da kasancewa a nan gaba shi ne, Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a fagen, zuwa ga babban jami'in da ke cikin sabis ɗin rashin jin daɗi - wani ƙaramin aiki ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan zai zama ƙarshen firaministan da yake da babban matsayi kuma yana da babban aiki, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken rushewar shahararsa ta siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin iyakar ƙoƙarinta tare da wannan ɗan wasan kwaikwayo na Teresa-May amma rubutun ba ya ba da aiki sosai.
Mai ba ta shawara a kan harkokin leken asiri ya gaya mata cewa idan kowane ɗan leken asiri yana aiki, dole ne ta yi amfani da wani da ya yi ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English mai zurfi a cikin babban mutum, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata cibiyar da ta fi dacewa, amma yana ba da darussan ba bisa hukuma ba game da aikin ɓoye a gefe.
An tura English zuwa Whitehall don ganawa na gaggawa kuma an sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai tsawon rai Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya auri wani jirgin ruwa mai suna U-boat, wani wasan hockey mai ban sha'awa wanda Vicki Pepperdine ke kusa da zubar da shi.
Sai Batman da Robin suka dawo bayan da komai ya tafi daidai ba daidai ba a cikin Sirrin Her Majesty kuma sun haɗu da Olga Kurylenko, kyakkyawar matar Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista zai yi fama da wani mutum mai suna Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya taka rawa.
English da Bough sun fara wasan kwaikwayon da suka yi na baƙon abu: suna yin ado da masu hidima, suna ƙona wuta a wani gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban sha'awa; suna haifar da rikici yayin da suke fashi a kan jirgin ruwa mai ban sha'awa na Volta; kuma English yana haifar da lalataccen rikici yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da VR-headset don gano abin da ke ciki na gidan Volta.
Hakika, akwai aiki mai yawa a bayan wannan fim ɗin, amma duk da cewa fim ɗin yana da kyau kuma yana da saurin gudu, yana da talabijin na yara a kusa da shi.
A cikin matsakaici, duk abin da.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ba zan iya yin tunani ba: Shin, masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson wani rawar da ta dace da baiwarsa ba?
Labour ta musanta cewa an tsara shirin da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki na kwana hudu a mako amma su samu albashi na kwana biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn tana tunanin shirin da zai sa Birtaniya ta yi aiki na kwana hudu a mako amma a biya ta biyar.
A cewarsa, jam'iyyar ta bukaci shugabannin kamfanoni su ba da kuɗin da suka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha ta wucin gadi ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su karin ranar hutu.
Za a yi hakan don a yi wa ma'aikatan hidima hutu na kwana uku amma a ci gaba da biyan su albashin da suka yi.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "dace" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar don amfanin ma'aikata.
Hukumar kwadago ta Trades Union Congress ta amince da sauya zuwa mako na kwana huɗu a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su amfana daga canje-canjen tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in Labor ya gaya wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa ana sa ran za a buga wannan binciken kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba za a yi hakan a rana ɗaya ba, amma mako na aiki na kwana huɗu ƙoƙari ne da ya dace da halin da jam'iyyar take ciki na daidaita tattalin arzikin don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance ta farko ba da ke goyon bayan irin wannan ra'ayin, har ma da jam'iyyar The Greens da ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben ta 2017.
Amma, Labour ba ta amince da wannan manufa ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun Labour ya ce: "Babu manufa ta jam'iyyar ba ce, kuma ba abu ne da jam'iyyar ta amince da shi".
Shugaba John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron Labour na makon da ya gabata don ya bayyana ra'ayinsa game da juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar karbar ikon "shugabannin da ba su da fuska" da kuma "masu-kusa" a kamfanonin gwamnati.
Shadow Chancellor's plans kuma na nufin cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu a cikin kamfanonin ruwa ba za su iya samun cikakken hannun jari ba, saboda gwamnatin Labour na iya yin 'karɓar' saboda abin da suka ɗauka ba daidai ba ne.
Ya kuma tabbatar da shirin sanya ma'aikata a cikin hukumar kamfanoni da kuma samar da abin da ake kira Inclusive Ownership Funds inda kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu za a mika wa ma'aikatan su, wanda a lokacin zai sami rabon shekara-shekara har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy suna magana a shirin talabijin na "60 Minutes" game da ko binciken da FBI ta yi kan Kavanaugh zai iya canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI game da zargin da ake yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben karshe na nadin sa a kotun koli da akalla mako guda, kuma ya kawo batun ko binciken hukumar zai iya sa wasu Sanatocin Republican su sauya ra'ayi a kan batun.
A wata hira da aka yi da jaridar "60 Minutes", mai ba da rahoto Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin 'yan Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya yi kama da wanda ya fi sa ido a kan batun.
"Tabbas", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce a lokacin da na shiga cikin sauraron, na yi magana da Alkali Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan an yi hakan, bayan an bayyana wannan ikirarin, na ce, "Ka yi hakan?"
Ya kasance mai ƙuduri, mai tabbaci, marar tabbaci".
Amma muryar Graham ba ta da ƙarfi.
"Na riga na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma hakan zai bukaci a tuhume ni da wani abu mai kama da sinadarin dinamite", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta hakan sosai", in ji Graham, yana mai da hankali ga Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk sunayen da ta ambata ba su tabbatar da hakan ba.
Shekaru 36 ne da suka shige.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu ya canja".
Mene ne bikin Global Citizen, kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke ɗauke da tarin taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma irin wannan aikin da ke da ban sha'awa: yaƙi da talaucin duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane suna yawo a babban lambu na Central Parks, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron: magance talauci mai tsanani kafin shekara ta 2030.
A cewar wata sanarwa da aka fitar a shekarar 2012, bikin na Global Citizen Festival na cigaba ne da shirin Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan yaki da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da ta.
Don samun tikiti kyauta na taron (idan ba ka shirya biyan tikitin VIP ba), baƙi za su yi ayyuka da yawa, ko kuma "aiki" kamar aikin agaji, aikawa da imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don su sa mutane su san cewa za a kawar da talauci.
Amma, yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu ta kasance da shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta kyauta kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta rinjayar mutane su yi aiki, ko kuwa kawai abin da ake kira "clicktivism" ne - mutane da suke jin cewa suna yin babban canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan aikace-aikacen kan layi ko kuma rubuta tweet?
Tun daga shekara ta 2011, Global Citizen ta ce an rubuta fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" na mabiyanta da suka yi gwagwarmaya don dalilai da dama.
An ce waɗannan matakan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37, kuma hakan zai shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ba da alkawuran da sanarwar 390 da suka fito daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 suka riga sun biya ko aka ba da gudummawa.
Ƙungiyar ta kiyasta cewa dukiyar da aka tara ta yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran su ne The Power of Nutrition, wani haɗin gwiwar da ke Burtaniya tsakanin masu saka jari da masu aiki da ke aiki don "taimaka yara su ci gaba zuwa ga cikakkiyar damarsu", wanda ya yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa wajen magance rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin bayan ya sami tweets fiye da 4,700 daga 'yan ƙasa na duniya.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Birtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya, kamar ku, za mu iya yin rashin adalci na zamantakewa wanda rashin abinci mai gina jiki ya zama sanarwa a tarihi", in ji Jakadan Kamfanin Tracey Ullman ga taron jama'a a wani taro na raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka ɗauki matakan da suka bukaci Birtaniya ta inganta abincin mata da yara fiye da 5,000, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade don aikin, Power of Nutrition, wanda ya ƙunshi shirye-shiryen abinci ga mata da yara miliyan 5.
A cikin amsar wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafinsa: "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya magance matsanancin talauci?"
Sai Global citizen ya amsa: "Wannan zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala - a wasu lokatai za mu yi kasawa kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan 'yancin bil adama da kuma 'yan adawa da wariyar launin fata da suka riga mu, za mu yi nasara, domin mun fi karfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin wasu daga cikin masu yin wasan kwaikwayo a wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman suka shirya.
Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa a cikin "tashin" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha, Ministan Harkokin Cikin Gida ya ce
Gwamnatin Amirka za ta iya amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa "idan ya cancanta" don hana masu amfani da makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwanni, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Ministan Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amirka, Ryan Zinke, wanda Washington Examinator ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha a Syria - musamman ma inda take aiki a kan gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace ta yi - wani abin zargi ne don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ya ce: "Ina ganin suna cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya domin suna son sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai".
Ya ce akwai hanyoyin da za a magance matsalar.
Ya ce: "Amurka tana da ikon, ta hanyar rundunarmu ta jiragen ruwa, ta tabbatar da cewa jiragen ruwa suna buɗewa kuma idan ya cancanta, ta yi amfani da shinge don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba ya kaiwa kasuwa".
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar ta Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai neman tallafi da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, kuma ya lura cewa sun yi daidai.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shi ne, aƙalla, amfani da kuma musayar man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai da hankali ga Rasha a matsayin "ƙasar rana" da tattalin arzikinta ya dogara da man fetur.
Sanarwar ta zo ne bayan gwamnatin Trump ta yi niyyar ƙara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, don maye gurbin Rasha, wadda ta fi araha ga masu amfani da Turai.
A wannan dalili, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna ƙoƙarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama "mazaunin" Moscow.
A cewar Moscow, aikin da ake yi na samar da bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 mai dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin da ake da shi zuwa mita 110 biliyan, aikin tattalin arziki ne.
Sun ce rashin amincewar Washington da wannan aikin na da dalilai na tattalin arziki ne kawai kuma misali ne na rashin gaskiya.
"Ina ganin muna da ra'ayin da ya dace cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki na matsa lamba ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su zaɓi masu samar da kayayyaki", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
An yi watsi da ra'ayin Amurka daga Jamus, wadda ta tabbatar da cewa ta yi aiki sosai a kan wannan aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta bukaci Amurka ta guji shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Na yi matukar fushi da yadda wani ɓangare na uku zai hana mu samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban hukumar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da Shugaba Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin suka yi.
Elizabeth Warren za ta dauki "mai tunani mai kyau" idan ta tsaya takara a zaben shugaban kasa na 2020, in ji Sanata na Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi "tunanin gaske" game da halartar zaben shugaban kasa bayan zaben Amurka na tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron majalisar dattijai a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da takarar.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya haɗa da mace a saman", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi wa shugaban kasa Donald Trump ba'a a taron majalisar, ya ce "ya kai wannan kasa cikin mummunan hanya.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
