An Sake Sake Sake Sake Sake Jirgin Sojin Jamus
An ce an tura sabon jirgin ruwa na rundunar sojin Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na lokacin yakin sanyi, amma ba za a fara aiki ba har zuwa aƙalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsari da tsada, kafofin watsa labarai na yankin sun ruwaito.
An dage aikin da ake yi na jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz, wanda ya zama jagorar sabon jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa rabin shekarar 2019, in ji jaridar Die Zeit, da ke ambaton wani mai magana da yawun soja.
Ya kamata a yi amfani da jirgin a cikin jirgin ruwa a shekara ta 2014, amma matsalolin da suka taso bayan isarwa sun lalace ga wannan babban aikin.
Jirgin ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta yi umurni da su a shekara ta 2007 za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Za su ƙunshi makami mai ƙarfi, wasu makamai masu linzami da na jiragen ruwa, da wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa, kamar su radar da ke ƙasa, infrared da kuma siginar sauti.
Sauran muhimman ayyuka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - ya kamata a iya sanya sabbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu ba tare da haɗuwa da tashar jiragen ruwa ba.
Amma, a cikin wani labari na gaba, jiragen ruwa masu amfani da jiragen ruwa na zamani - waɗanda ke ba Jamus damar yin amfani da ikonta a ƙasashen waje - sun riga sun tsufa a lokacin da aka soma amfani da su, in ji Die Zeit.
Freget din F125 mai lalacewa ya yi sanarwa a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojan Jamus ta ƙi shigar da jirgin a cikin aiki kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta mayar da wani jirgin zuwa wani mai gina jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilan da suka sa aka yi wannan yaƙi ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ba da rahoton wasu muhimman "rashin software da kayan aiki" da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi a aikin yaƙi.
Ƙarshen software na musamman yana da muhimmanci domin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan mazauna kimanin 120 - rabin ma'aikatan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma nuna cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke haifar da lalacewar aikin da kuma iyakance ikon da rundunar jiragen ruwa ke da shi na yin ci gaba.
An yi zaton jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin da na wasu jiragen ruwa da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da kayan aiki mara kyau, duk farashin aikin, gami da horar da ma'aikatan, zai zama matsala.
An ce adadin ya kai na Euro biliyan 3.1 (dalar Amurka biliyan 3.6) - idan aka kwatanta da na Euro biliyan 2.2 a farkon shekara.
Matsalolin da ke shafan sabbin jiragen ruwa na jirgin ruwa na musamman suna da muhimmanci sosai a cikin yanayin da ake nuna cewa ƙarfin teku na Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekara, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, Hans-Peter Bartels, ya yarda cewa a zahiri rundunar jiragen ruwa "ta soma rashin jiragen ruwa masu cikakken kayan aiki".
Jami'in ya ce wannan matsala ce mai girma, saboda ana soke tsofaffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da su a matsayin masu maye gurbin su ba.
Ya yi nadama cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa.
