Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta afku a birnin Palu, Indonesia, a ranar Juma'a, jami'an gwamnati sun ce.
Ba a samu bayanai daga yankin Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu da ke kusa da inda aka yi girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 a kan sikelin Richter.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palu bayan wannan bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, kuma yana cikin wani bakin teku mai yalwa a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala yanki ne na gudanarwa wanda ke da nisan fiye da kilomita 300 daga arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A shekarar 2017, yankin da ake gudanarwa, wanda shi ne yanki na gudanarwa a karkashin wani lardin, ya kai yawan mutane kimanin 299,200.
Kasashen da ke kula da tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya sune kifi da gona, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Harkokin nickel na da mahimmanci a lardin, amma yana da mahimmanci a Morowali, a gefen Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya yi wa yankin yammacin Donggala rauni kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yanayin girgizar ƙasa na yankin Pacific, wanda yawanci girgizar ƙasa ke damunta.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani babban girgizar ƙasa a yammacin yankin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14. Mutane 226,000 suka mutu a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya. Fiye da rabin su sun kasance a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin bakin teku na Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
A shekara ta 2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 a kan sikelin Richter ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da ya fi kowa yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya afkawa kudu da ke kudu da tekun, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai a bakin Sumatra. An yi tsunami mai tsayi har mita 10, an lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma an kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici, lokacin da aka tunatar da mutane game da halakar da ta faru a cikin mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma gine-gine sun rushe kuma sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane fiye da 500 suka mutu, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine, kuma dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun bar teku a wani lokaci.
An kama ɗansa na farko, Sarah Palin, da ake zargi da aikata mugunta a gida
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, an kama shi bisa zargin cin zarafin da ake masa.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin yin amfani da zalunci a gida, da kuma yin magana game da yin hakan, a cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce ya karɓi wayar daga wata mace da ya san ta da ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton laifin da ake zargi.
An tsare Palin a gidan yari na Mat-Su, kuma ana tsare da shi a kan bashin dala 500 da za a biya idan wanda ake zargi ya karya sharuɗɗan bashin, a cewar tashar talabijin ta KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar kuma ya bayyana kansa a matsayin "mai tabbacin rashin laifi" lokacin da aka tambaye shi ya bayyana matsayinsa, a cewar tashar talabijin.
Ana zargin Palin da aikata laifuka guda uku na ƙaramar aji A, wanda ke nufin yana iya yin kurkuku har zuwa shekara guda da kuma tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da aikata wani laifi mai tsanani kamar na B, wanda ake yi wa hukuncin ɗaurin kurkuku na kwana ɗaya da kuma tarar dala 2,000.
Ba wannan ba ne karo na farko da ake zargi Palin da aikata laifi.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge shi da aikata laifi a kan mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton abin da ake zargi da aikata.
Kotun Alaska ta kula da batun.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da aikata laifuka a gida, da shigar da rahoton aikata laifuka a gida, da kuma mallakar makamai a lokacin da yake cikin tasiri a cikin wannan lamarin.
Yarinyarsa ta zarge shi da ya buge ta a fuska.
A shekarar 2016, 'yan bindiga sun soki Sarah Palin saboda ta danganta halin da ɗanta ya nuna da rashin jin daɗi da ya samu daga aikinsa a Iraqi.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Mutane Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afku a tsibirin Sulawesi a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa da ta kai sikelin Richter 7.5 ta jawo tsunami kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
Rashin wutar lantarki da kuma hanyoyin sadarwa na cikin ƙasa, kuma ana sa ran yawan mutuwar zai tashi a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ƙasa ta afku a wajen Sulawesi ta tsakiya, arewa maso gabashin Jakarta, babban birnin ƙasar Indonesia.
Yanzu ana samun hotunan da ke nuna lokacin da ya faru a shafukan sada zumunta.
Dubban mutane sun taru a wani biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu sa'ad da tsunami ya afku a bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yi masa hukuncin kisa na musamman don wani wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York sun bukaci a yi masa hukuncin kisa don Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da wata babbar motar haya daga gidan gine-gine da kuma kayan ado na Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke a kan West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan.
Don a yi musu hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara suna bukatar su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda suka mutu takwas kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a kotun ta Kudu ta New York.
Dukkanin tuhumar da aka yi da su na iya sa a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda kotun ta ce.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, wata juriya ta tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da zargi 22, ciki har da shari'o'i takwas na kisan kai don tallafawa ayyukan tsaro, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma cin zarafi da lalata motocin.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci tsari da kuma niyya, kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai shi a matsayin abin ƙyama, da zalunci da kuma rashin mutuntaka.
Sanarwar ta ce, Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa danginsa da abokansa lahani da lahani, kamar Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance 'yan yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Ba a kai karar da kotun kudancin New York ta shigar ba a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
An kashe su ne a shekarar 1953 a kotun tarayya a birnin New York. An kashe su ne bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a lokacin da suka yi wa Soviet ta'aziyya a lokacin yakin sanyi shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe Ma'aurata Rosenberg a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda ɗan ƙasar Uzbek ne, ya nuna cewa bai tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa abin da ya yi ya gamsar da shi.
A cewar alƙali, Saipov ya gaya wa hukumomi cewa ya sami wahayi zuwa harin bayan ya kalli bidiyon IS a wayarsa.
Ya kuma nemi a saka tutar IS a dakinsa a asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan tuhuma 22 da ake tuhuma da shi.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya bayyana cewa sun yi matukar takaici da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon a yi masa hukuncin daurin rai ba tare da yiwuwar a sake shi ba idan wanda ake tuhuma ya yarda da laifinsa ya yi laifi ya kara yawan raunin da waɗannan abubuwan suka jawo ga dukan waɗanda suka yi", in ji Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar masu kare hakkin Saipov ta roƙi masu gabatar da kara kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
'Yan Tory sun ce dole ne NIGEL FARAGE ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin karfafa rundunar sojin kasarsa a yau a wani zanga-zanga a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban UKIP ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su fahimci halin da ake ciki na masu shakka a kan EU lokacin da wani dan majalisa na Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa zai jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisar dokoki mai suna Peter Bone ya ce a lokacin da ake gudanar da zanga-zangar a Birmingham, Birtaniya ta riga ta yi watsi da shi idan Nigel Farage ya zama ministan Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Theresa May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta masu goyon bayan da ke da rabuwa da juna ya kara muni da 'yan majalisar Turai masu fa'ida, wadanda suka shiga wani zanga-zanga na musamman na Brexit a birnin.
Firayim Minista yana gwagwarmaya don kiyaye shirinsa na sulhu, yarjejeniyar Chequers, a raye a lokacin da ake kai hari daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, mutanen da suke son su kasance a cikin Tarayyar Turai da kuma EU kanta.
Abokan tarayyarta sun nace cewa ta kamata ta matsa lamba kuma ta yi kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da rashin nasara, kuma ta tilasta masu shakka game da EU da Labour Party su zabi tsakanin ta shirya bayani da kuma kaos.
Bone ya ce a wani taro da kungiyar Leave Means Leave ta shirya a Solihull cewa yana son ya yi yarjejeniyar Chequers.
Ya nuna cewa ya kamata a daidaita Nigel Farage kuma a ba shi alhakin tattaunawar da ke faruwa a Brussels.
Ya ce, "Da a ce yana tsaye a bakin dutsen, da mun fita a wannan lokacin".
Peter Bone, wanda ke wakiltar gundumar Wellingborough a majalisar dokokin kasar ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu soke yarjejeniyar Chequers".
Ya bayyana rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi ba domin mu zama talakawa.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.
Bone ya yi watsi da zargin cewa jama'a sun canza tun bayan zaben 2016: Tunanin cewa Birtaniya sun canza kuma yanzu suna so su zauna ba gaskiya bane.
Wanda ya yi magana da 'yan jarida a lokacin da ake gudanar da zanga-zangar shi ne mai goyon bayan Brexit, Andrea Jenkyns na jam'iyyar Tory.
Yarjejeniyar Chequers ba ta da kyau a wurin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi ta ba, ba ta da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan wasanmu na zabe da ke kan titi suna sa mu a zabe.
Ka bar yarjejeniyar Chequers kuma ka fara sauraro.
Ta kuma kara da cewa, tana da wata sanarwa mai karfi ga Theresa May: "Primeers suna da damar rike aikinsu idan sun cika alkawarin da suka yi".
Nigel Farage ya ce a taron dole ne 'yan siyasa su ji zafi idan za su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a lokacin zaben 2016.
Ya ce, "Yanzu batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu, wato, mutane, da kuma 'yan siyasa.
Suna kokarin yaudarar Brexit, kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu: Ba za mu bar ku kubuta da hakan ba.
A gaban taron masu farin ciki, ya ce: "Ina so ku sa ku ji daɗin rayuwarmu ta siyasa, wadda ta kusa ƙin amincewa da Brexit.
Muna tattara rundunar al'umma a wannan kasar da ta ba mu nasara a Brexit, kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta, da kuma girman kai Birtaniya.
A lokaci guda, masu goyon bayan EU sun yi ta yawo a birnin Birmingham, sannan suka yi taron jama'a na tsawon sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan adawa sun yi ta yin waƙoƙi da rubutun 'Masu garkuwa da 'yan kungiyar' bayan an kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Dan majalisar Labour, Lord Adonis na majalisar dattijai, ya yi wa 'yan majalisa ba'a game da matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta ta hanyar yin amfani da app na jam'iyyar a lokacin da taron ya buɗe.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT a wurin da duk fasahar Kanada da kuma yarjejeniyar da ke ciki, don iyaka marar iyaka da kuma cinikayya ta kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", ya kara da cewa.
"Wannan uba ne mai tsarki.
Ya kara da cewa, babu wani Brexit mai kyau.
Warren yana shirin yin tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa 'yan majalisa 'yan Democrat daga Massachusetts sun tattauna game da makomarsu a wani taron majalisar dokoki a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren ya yi ta sukar Shugaba Donald Trump sau da yawa, kuma yanzu yana neman sake zabarsa a watan Nuwamba a kan ɗan takarar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya kasance mataimakin shugaban yakin neman zaben Donald Trump a Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
An yi ta tunanin cewa za ta iya zama shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020.
Wannan taron da ya faru a ranar Asabar da yamma a birnin Holyoke shi ne taron majalisar dattijai na 36 da ta yi da masu jefa kuri'a tun lokacin da Donald Trump ya yi mulki.
Wani mutum ya tambaye ta ko tana shirin neman takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace.
An kama mutum da harbi na kisa na dan wasan kwando Sims daga LSU
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani wanda ake zargi da harbi na kashe dan wasan kwando na LSU, Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge sun sanar da cewa an kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a wani taron manema labarai da ya yi a karfe 11:00 na yammacin kasar Sin.
Sun fitar da wani bidiyo na harin da aka yi a ranar Juma'a don su taimaka wajen gano mutumin da aka gani a cikin hotunan.
An kashe Sims mai shekara 20 a kusa da harabar jami'ar kudancin Amirka a ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya ji rauni a kai kuma ya mutu daga wannan", in ji Sakataren 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a kafofin watsa labarai a ranar Asabar ta hanyar gidan labarai 247 sports.
Wayde ya yi tsakiya don ya kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, ya yarda cewa ya kasance a wurin kuma yana da makami, kuma ya yarda cewa ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wani abu ba kuma an kai shi gidan yari a East Baton Rouge.
Sims dan wasan junior ne, mai tsayin mita 198 kuma ya girma a Baton Rouge. Ya buga wasanni 32 tare da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta karshe, yana da matsakaicin minti 17.4, maki 5.6, da kuma sake dawowa 2.9 a kowace wasa.
Gasar cin kofin Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusan lashe gasar cin kofin duniya bayan da ya lashe gasar Sebastian Vettel
Tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi nasara a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar, ya bayyana sarai cewa umurnin ƙungiyar Mercedes zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin tseren.
