Flowers: Ruwa a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ta fitar kwanan nan ya nuna cewa yawan algae da ke yawo a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
Hukumar ta ce an samu rashin daidaituwa a yankunan da ke kewaye da manyan biranen Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda zai iya nuna raguwar yawan.
Wannan furen ya yi nisan mil 20 daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
Ana iya ganin tabo a wajen mil da rabi a cikin teku a wajen garin Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da fure-fure a babban birnin Pasco.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, an samu rahoton matsakaitan matakan da aka kai a cikin Pinellas ko kuma a wajen tekun.
Rahotanni na rashin numfashi na ci gaba da zuwa daga manyan biranen Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Babu rahoton cutar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
